reviews.text: Food is tasty. The staff is really nice. Relaxing vibe with soft music. There are board games provided which is suitable for hanging out with friends and party

Only a few tables but cosy atmosphere. Nice place to talk as not crowded most of the time. Good food but takes quite a long time to come. Nice people who cooked and served. We were even given fruits to take back home as gifts. Good place to do family functions or parties.
Good food, reasonable price. Location is central in Tsimshatsui. One can easily spend a few hours there, relaxing & enjoying the time with friends.
